            <q>The warrant may be executed even if neither the warrant nor a copy of it is in the possession of the person executing it at the time of the arrest".</q></p><p>
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_314gc' title='Col. 314GC &mdash; HL Deb 18 June 2003 vol 649 c314GC' name='column_314gc' href='#column_314gc' rel='bookmark'>314GC</a>
