          <p class='first-para'>
            If the Minister were Sheriff Bassam, I believe that he would be very glad to have the <span class="italic">aide memoire</span> of the words that the sheriff must have reasonable grounds. He would know that he had to have reason and not just be swayed by an interesting argument.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0649P0-03865'>
        <a name='S5LV0649P0_20030618_GCR_182'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-kenneth-wedderburn' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030618_GCR_182' title='Link to this speech by Mr Kenneth Wedderburn' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
